1. Filter by Job Title

SELECT * FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE EMPJOB = 'MANAGER';

2. Filter by Salary Range

SELECT * FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE EMPSALARY BETWEEN 20000 AND 60000;

3. Filter by Hire Date (Before a Certain Date)

SELECT * FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE EMP_HIREDATE < '2015-01-01';

4. Filter by Multiple Conditions (e.g., Job + Salary)

SELECT * FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE EMPJOB = 'CLERK' AND EMPSALARY > 15000;

5. Filter Employees Hired in a Specific Year

SELECT * FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE YEAR(EMP_HIREDATE) = 2010;

6. Get Highest Paid Employee

SELECT * FROM EMPLOYEE ORDER BY EMPSALARY DESC LIMIT 1;

7. General Search System (Using LIKE)

SELECT * FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE EMPNAME LIKE '%A%';
